response.overview: The Bibbulmun Track is one of the world’s great long distance trails, winding over 1,000km through the heart of scenic southwest Western Australia.  Join the incredible Erika Lori as she sets off to run about 100kms per day and battle the sandy beaches, dense forests and wet marshland.  A journey like this wouldn’t be possible without support and Erika has that in spades with a big family of athletes you’ll fall in love with, friends who wanted to be a part of something bigger and even a romantic suitor!
response.title: BIBBULMUN FTK
